Acked-by: Thomas Bogendoerfer <tbogendoerfer@suse.de>
---
 drivers/infiniband/ulp/rtrs/rtrs-srv.h |  148 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 148 insertions(+)
